  ('social-worker-moex-02353', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '「剎車失靈的司機，為避免造成更大人員的傷亡，而選擇撞向人少的地方」。這種選擇比較傾向下列那 種倫理學立場？', '["效益論", "義務論", "德行論", "權利論"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9b8a3d37c0d1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5df06a1a485f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "107", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02354', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '「無論在何種情況下，社會工作者都應該持守尊重人這項原則」。以上說法，比較傾向下列那種倫理學 立場？', '["效益論", "義務論", "德行論", "權利論"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9b8a3d37c0d1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5df06a1a485f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "107", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02355', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'essay', '近日有民代指控社工人員，質疑遊民服務事件；過去也曾有角頭老大殺死親生女兒，
